OL,3,CBus driver dies in crash involving
OL,4,Cschool children
OL,6,FPolice have confirmed that the driver
OL,7,Fof a bus involved in a single vehicle
OL,8,Fcrash in County Armagh on Tuesday has
OL,9,Fdied.
OL,11,FThe bus was carrying 40 pupils from St
OL,12,FPaul's High School in Bessbrook. The
OL,13,Fprincipal has confirmed that none of
OL,14,Fthem were seriously injured. The crash
OL,15,Fhappened in the Tullyah Road area of
OL,16,FBelleeks between Newtownhamilton and
OL,17,FCamlough.
