OL,6,FThe police said that the driver of the
OL,7,Fbus sadly died at the scene. The road
OL,8,Fwas closed for a period of time but
OL,9,Fhas since reopened.
OL,11,FIt is understood the incident is being
OL,12,Ftreated as a sudden death.
OL,14,FIn a statement on social media, Quinn
OL,15,FCoaches, confirmed that one of its
OL,16,Fdrivers had died in the crash.
OL,18,FThe statement said: "Our first
OL,19,Fthoughts are with his family, friends,
OL,20,Fand fellow colleagues during this
OL,21,Fincredibly difficult time.
