OL,6,F"He was a respected and experienced
OL,7,Fmember of our team, and he will be
OL,8,Fgreatly missed."
OL,10,FIn a letter to parents on Tuesday, the
OL,11,FPrincipal of St Paul's High School Mr
OL,12,FMurray said: "I am writing to make you
OL,13,Faware of a serious incident that took
OL,14,Fplace on school transport this
OL,15,Fafternoon (Tuesday) as pupils were
OL,16,Fmaking their way home.
