OL,6,F"We have ascertained that all pupils
OL,7,Fare safe and have been collected by
OL,8,Ftheir parents. We appreciate that this
OL,9,Fwill have caused a signficant shock to
OL,10,Fpupils who experienced the incident.
OL,12,F"The school has sought advice and
OL,13,Fguidance from the Education
OL,14,FAuthority's Critical Incident Response
OL,15,FTeam (CIRT) and personnel from this
OL,16,Fteam will be available to support
OL,17,Fpupils affected by the incident
OL,18,Ftomorrow.
